Prototype 1:

Downloads:
Arduino
download libraries- adafruit BusIO, adafruit MLX90614

Install python
https://www.python.org/downloads

Install pyserial
https://pypi.org/project/pyserial

Open command prompt on your computer, you need to install a few libraries. Type:
pip install pyserial
pip install pandas
pip install matplotlib

To run the code, download the arduino and python file posted. Once arduino is opened, upload and run it but do not open serial monitor. 

Open command prompt and type in:
cd downloads
python griddisplay.py






